# Component Development Patterns

## Component Architecture
- Follow the existing patterns in [src/components/](mdc:src/components/)
- Use composition over inheritance
- Keep components small and focused
- Use proper TypeScript interfaces for props

## UI Components
- Use shadcn/ui components from [src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui/)
- Extend shadcn/ui components when needed
- Follow the design system established in [components.json](mdc:components.json)
- Use Lucide React icons consistently

## Activity Components
- Follow patterns from [ActivityCard.tsx](mdc:src/components/ActivityCard.tsx)
- Use [ActivityImage.tsx](mdc:src/components/ActivityImage.tsx) for image handling
- Implement proper loading states and error handling
- Use the Activity interface from [src/lib/types.ts](mdc:src/lib/types.ts)

## Map Integration
- Follow the pattern in [InteractiveMap.tsx](mdc:src/components/InteractiveMap.tsx)
- Use proper Mapbox GL JS integration
- Handle dynamic imports for Mapbox
- Implement proper marker management and event handling

## Carousel Components
- Use Swiper for carousels as in [ActivityCarousel.tsx](mdc:src/components/ActivityCarousel.tsx)
- Implement proper responsive behavior
- Handle touch/swipe interactions
- Use proper accessibility attributes